#Roadmap
Define the AMateria class:

Define the constructor and the necessary member functions.
Define the pure virtual function clone() and the virtual function use().
Define the concrete classes Ice and Cure:

Inherit from AMateria.
Implement the clone() method.
Implement the use() method.
Define the ICharacter interface:

Define the pure virtual functions: getName(), equip(), unequip(), and use().
Implement the Character class:

Inherit from ICharacter.
Manage an inventory of AMateria objects.
Implement the necessary member functions.
Define the IMateriaSource interface:

Define the pure virtual functions: learnMateria() and createMateria().
Implement the MateriaSource class:

Inherit from IMateriaSource.
Manage a list of learned AMateria objects.
Implement the necessary member functions.
